/ Page Content
#more_info
.content-section-b
  .clearfix
  .container
    %div.row
      .col-sm-12.col-md-4.col-md-offset-4
        -#
          %p.text-center
            %i.fa.fa-chevron-circle-up.fa-3x
        = image_tag("syd_transparent_metal_logo_624x351.jpg", class: 'img-responsive')
    %div.row
      %div.col-sm-12
        .well
          %h1.text-center DragonDOG Free
          .lead
            %p
              DragonDOG Free is a web application allowing scrap professionals to record transactions, documents and pictures on TranAct’s shared server for <b>free</b>.  
              Your company will be created upon signup and all users will use the same login and password. Your single login can be used by any number of users at 
              the same time on computers or mobile devices.
            %p
              Your DragonDOG company has a list of default commodities which you’ll want to edit and price prior to getting started.  All your data is available 
              for management reporting and uploading to Leads Online. Your data is stored in a Scrap Dragon format so upgrades are available for the entire 
              TranAct® product line.
          .text-center
            %ul.list-inline
              %li
                %i.fa.fa-mobile-phone.fa-5x
              %li
                %i.fa.fa-tablet.fa-5x
              %li
                %i.fa.fa-desktop.fa-5x
      -#
        %div.col-sm-6
          .well
            %h1.text-center The Smart Way to Buy Scrap
            .lead
              %p
                Forget hand writing tickets or clumsy programs, Dragon Dog's friendly interface can be used by anyone. Scale operators will be buying scrap 
                within minutes of signup, and once entered, the data is available for management reporting and uploading to Leads Online.
              %p
                Dragon Dog is a FREE web interface for scrap yards to buy scrap using any mobile device or computer. Pictures can be taken with mobile device and added 
                to tickets for compliance and retention. All data is hosted at our state-of-the-art data hosting facility. Easily 
                view transactions and commodity reports for business planning and daily review.
      .text-center
        %p
          =# link_to 'Learn More', 'https://tranact.com/freescrapbuying/', class: 'btn btn-lg btn-default', target: '_blank'
          = link_to 'Sign Up for Free!', 'https://sdx.scrapyarddog.com/signup', class: 'btn btn-lg btn-warning'

    %div.row
      %div.col-sm-4
        .well
          .text-center
            %i.fa.fa-hand-pointer-o.fa-5x
            %p.lead 
              Simplified buttons control all aspects of using Dragon Dog.
          %ul
            %li Commodity List Provided
            %li Create Custom Contracts
            %li Customize Viewable Settings
            %li Easily Edit Customers
            %li Take Pictures with Mobile Device
            %li Easy Ticket Management
        = image_tag('SYD-Home-Screen.png', class: 'img-responsive center-block')

      %div.col-sm-4.col-md-4
        .well
          .text-center
            %i.fa.fa-user.fa-5x
            %p.lead View tickets and review or create new customers easily.
          %ul
